  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ireland supported a programme of technical assistance to the Ministry of Community Development and Social Welfare through four UN Agencies; ILO, WFP, UNICEF and IOM, led by UNICEF. The programme focuses on systems strengthening and human resource capacity development within the Ministries engaged in the broader social protection schemes in the country.</narrative>
  </description>
